Package: decomp
Type: Package
Title: Various functions to quantify and decompose health inequalities
Version: 0.3
Date: 2009-08-26
Author: Peter Konings and Niko Speybroeck
Maintainer: Peter Konings <peter.konings@esat.kuleuven.be>
Description: This package contains functions to calculate the relative concentration index,
	plot Lorenz curves and decompose inequality using (generalized) linear models and survival models while
	taking survey design into account.
License: GPL 2.0 or later
LazyLoad: yes
Suggests: gplots
